---
title: "checkUpkeep (BaseAuction - inherited by GPV2CompatibleAuction)"
---
stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB
    [*] --> q_init: load feeAggregator, allowlisted assets
    q_init --> q_iter: i = 0
    q_iter --> q_load_asset: i < auctions.length
    q_load_asset --> q_skip: assetParams.decimals == 0
    q_skip --> q_next: skip unconfigured asset
    q_load_asset --> q_get_price: _getAssetPrice(asset, false)
    q_get_price --> q_check_assetout: asset == s_assetOut
    q_check_assetout --> q_save_price_valid: isAssetOutPriceValid = isPriceValid
    q_check_assetout --> q_check_live: auctionStart != 0
    q_save_price_valid --> q_check_live: auctionStart != 0
    q_check_live --> q_check_ended: auctionStart + duration < timestamp OR balance USD < minAuctionSize
    q_check_ended --> q_add_ended: condition met
    q_add_ended --> q_next: endedAuctions[idx++] = asset
    q_check_ended --> q_next: auction still live
    q_check_live --> q_check_eligible: auctionStart == 0 AND isPriceValid
    q_check_eligible --> q_check_usd: availableAssetUsdValue >= minAuctionSizeUsd
    q_check_usd --> q_add_eligible: eligibleAssets[idx++] = (asset, balance)
    q_add_eligible --> q_next
    q_check_usd --> q_next: below min auction size
    q_check_eligible --> q_next: price not valid
    q_next --> q_iter: i = i + 1
    q_iter --> q_assetout_gate: i >= auctions.length
    q_assetout_gate --> q_clear_eligible: isAssetOutPriceValid == false
    q_clear_eligible --> q_encode: eligibleAssetsIdx = 0
    q_assetout_gate --> q_encode: isAssetOutPriceValid == true
    q_encode --> q_return_true: eligibleAssetsIdx > 0 OR endedAuctionsIdx > 0
    q_return_true --> [*]: return (true, abi.encode(eligibleAssets, endedAuctions))
    q_encode --> [*]: return (false, empty bytes)

    note right of q_init
        INV-001: No auctions are started if assetOut price is invalid
        INV-002: Auctions end when duration elapsed OR remaining balance USD < minAuctionSize
        INV-003: Only assets with configured params (decimals != 0) are considered
        INV-004: Eligible assets must have valid price and USD balance above minAuctionSizeUsd
    end note
